title: Milan Kundera - Identity (pdf)
description:
Milan Kundera - Identity (HarperCollins, 1998). 168 pages.

New scan. Searchable pdf (clearscan) with accurate pagination and metadata, etc. No contents links seemed necessary in this one -- it's basically a novella divided into 51 short sections.


description from wikipedia:

Identity is a novel by Franco-Czech writer Milan Kundera, published in 1998. It is possibly his most traditional novel in terms of narrative structure. It's also one of his shortest novels.

The phrase "masturbating fetus" appears to have been coined in this novel.
